node.text:
#NEWS: The all-new, fully outfitted #G700 set its first two city-pair speed records during its maiden international voyage — Savannah to Doha and Doha to Paris. Carbon offsets are being applied for both flights.

✈️ Savannah to Doha: 6,711 nm/12,428 km | Mach 0.88 | 13h 16m
✈️Doha to Paris: 2,953 nm/5,469 km | Mach 0.90 | 6h 15m

More details at the #linkinbio.
